[normal]A
[normal] 
[normal]‘
[normal]prompt
[normal]’
[normal] is a
[normal] verbal, visual, written or recorded 
[normal]cue that reminds people to carry out a
[normal] specific
[normal] target behavio
[normal]ur
[normal].
[normal] A ‘normative message’ is a verbal, visual, written or recorded communication that contains information about 
[normal]what types of behaviours are typically performed
[normal] (
[normal]descriptive
[normal] 
[normal]norms
[normal]), what types of behaviour 
[normal]are 
[normal]socially approved or disapproved of (injunctive norms), or that appeals to a personal moral obligation to 
[normal]engage in a 
[normal]particular
[normal] behaviour (
[normal]personal norms).
